//Database Associations
	
	User - Has_many Post
		 - Has_many comments  
	UserAdmin - Single Table inherance 


	Post - Belongs_to User
		 - Has_many Comments


	Comments - Belongs_to Post
			 - Belongs_to User
	
//Attributes 

	User - First_name
		   Last_name
		   Email
		   type


    Post - Title
    	   Body
    	   Likes/Dislikes
    	   Date

    Comments - Body


